ger. 6. VICTORIOUS RULER did not attract much market support on debut but ran a beauty to finish third at Randwick-Kensington. From the inside gate, he has plenty of options, so stick with him on an each-way basis. 3. CAPITAL ILLUSION debuts with a strong pedigree. She won her latest trial with ease, and she will be ready to rumble, especially if the money comes for her.\",\"runners\":[1,2,6,3],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Darren Flindell","tipRunnerNumbers":[3,1,2,6]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,6,9]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,6,9]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,6,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,6,9]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,6,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,3,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,6,3]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":2,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"EarlyQuaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}}]}}}